Location is key, this home is 5 minutes from the Packing District, Orlando's hottest new area, close to all the major highways and attractions, Orlando Downtown, Amway Arena, Restaurants, a lot of Shoppings, Malls, Stores, Outlets, Universal Studios, and much more.
